
Spring scopes?

A bean is an object  of ioc inversion of controller there are 5 types of scopes

1 Singletone
2 Prototype
3 Request
4 Session
5 GlobalSession

SingleTone:-  one instance can be created all the container this is the default scope it will not thread safe

Prototype :- this can be create new request each and every time

Request :- this is similary to same as prototype it will be created new request each and every time

session : - A new request will be create each and every http request
